Language: en

00:00:13.132 --> 00:00:17.596
Hi Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:18.561 --> 00:00:24.264
What are you going to make?
I'm making Chicken 555

00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:32.045
Ingredients required to make Chicken 555

00:00:32.381 --> 00:00:47.618
Boneless Chicken, Maida Flour, Corn Flour, Pepper Powder, Tomato Ketchup, Tasting Salt,
 Eggs, Ginger &amp; Garlic, Green Chillies, Chilli Sauce, Cashews, Spring Onions, Salt, Oil

00:01:03.326 --> 00:01:08.137
Take 50 gms of maida flour

00:01:12.429 --> 00:01:18.819
Add 50 gms of corn flour to it

00:01:33.302 --> 00:01:39.793
Add one egg to the flour

00:01:46.477 --> 00:01:50.421
Meanwhile, take a pan and heat enough oil for deep frying

00:01:54.017 --> 00:01:57.738
Mix the egg in the flour

00:02:01.534 --> 00:02:06.254
Add a little white pepper powder
(You can use black pepper)

00:02:06.633 --> 00:02:14.370
Add a little ajinomoto and some salt for taste

00:02:19.043 --> 00:02:25.474
Add a little water and make a batter

00:02:34.015 --> 00:02:37.730
Make the batter with a watery consistency

00:02:49.784 --> 00:02:54.445
Dip the boneless chicken pieces in the batter

00:03:10.643 --> 00:03:18.089
Deep fry the batter dipped chicken

00:03:37.581 --> 00:03:44.959
Remove the chicken once they're fried to a light brown

00:03:57.659 --> 00:04:02.219
Take another pan and heat some oil

00:04:05.576 --> 00:04:10.913
Add a little finely chopped ginger &amp; garlic

00:04:16.166 --> 00:04:25.633
Add some finely chopped green chillies &amp; spring onions

00:04:32.519 --> 00:04:46.113
Add some tomato sauce/ketchup
and some green chilli sauce

00:04:51.567 --> 00:04:57.997
Add some cashews and some white pepper powder

00:05:01.390 --> 00:05:08.038
Add a little ajinomoto/tasting salt and
also add some salt for taste

00:05:20.553 --> 00:05:26.139
Add a little curd (1/2 cup)

00:05:48.250 --> 00:05:53.305
Add the batter fried chicken into the pan

00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:14.047
After cooking for 5 mins, take it off the stove

